Subject: [PATCH 1/3] LFU-944-1: frdm-imx95-pro: Add FRDM-IMX95-PRO board
 support

Add board level code and defconfig for FRDM-IMX95-PRO board.

Signed-off-by: Tom.zheng <haidong.zheng@nxp.com>
Signed-off-by: Joseph Guo <qijian.guo@nxp.com>
Reviewed-by: Ye Li <ye.li@nxp.com>
